{"tid":2022420,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★投資骨灰龕位---八年升五倍","createTime":"2020-05-18T10:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T12:17:23.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c33fdcf25fc13a4669eba806b5c7c76e004db756","tid":2022420,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T10:15:36.000Z","msg":"香港地皮短缺，不單人住的住宅貴，就連先人住的地方都價值不菲。因為香港公營骨灰位嚴重短缺，私營骨灰位發牌又進度緩慢，現在可謂一龕難求。很多人為求盡快令先人入土為安，都會高價買入龕位，所以幾年前開始多人投資骨灰位。從事龕位買賣已經接近10年的Kathrine，直指骨灰龕近幾年起碼升值五倍，今次有機會訪問她有關投資骨灰龕的事宜，更會在片內講述有關揀骨灰位的貼士。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BSN3dSgs8aI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBSN3dSgs8aI&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCgy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=92a4985a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BSN3dSgs8aI</a>"},{"pid":"44474d4ec8a0d73b165d9183d374475c8ee38987","tid":2022420,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T10:15:57.000Z","msg":"die more ,rise more<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e47c498e4def12f1c21b1c28af772cb49683b566","tid":2022420,"uid":325263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T10:16:13.000Z","msg":"算唔算發死人財"},{"pid":"f9fdfd3b87747a88ebfc9afa3cc8c82a2d5b1493","tid":2022420,"uid":277389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T10:16:17.000Z","msg":"（長文）（置頂）(戰術）金鐘野餐攻略 沙盤推演<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2018117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2018117</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nu6c2QF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnu6c2QF.jpg&h=61dc0e61&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6d0aa999dea41f31e0d72378ac74ae230fcd957